<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Welcome to FireTrack360</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4; color: #333; } .email-container { max-width:
      600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
      .email-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; } .email-header
      h1 { color: #2c3e50; } .email-body { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;
      color: #555; } .email-footer { margin-top: 20px; text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px; color: #888; } .button { display: inline-block;
      background-color: #3498db; color: #fff; padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <div class='email-container'>
      <div class='email-header'>
        <h1>Welcome to FireTrack360, {{firstName}}!</h1>
      </div>

      <div class='email-body'>
        <p>We're excited to have you on board. Your registration was successful,
          and you are now part of the FireTrack360 community!</p>

        <p>Here are some quick links to help you get started:</p>

        <ul>
          <li><a href='https://example.com/dashboard' class='button'>Go to
              Dashboard</a></li>
          <li><a href='https://example.com/help' class='button'>Help & Support</a></li>
        </ul>

        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at
          <a
            href='mailto:support@firetrack360.com'
          >support@firetrack360.com</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class='email-footer'>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The FireTrack360 Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>